            "type": "text",
            "text": "Security and reliability"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The adapter is the sole location where vendor credentials are used. Ensure credentials are injected via constructor arguments from a secrets manager\u2014never hard-coded or read from environment variables inside adapter methods where they may be logged."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Key takeaways"
          }
